data.description: Welcome to this charming home nestled on a spacious acre of lands, offering serene surroundings and privacy. Built in 2022, this modern gem features an unfinished basement, allowing you to customize and expand the living space according to your preferences. The master bedroom, with its generous size. provides a comfortable retreat. Situated in a quaint and peaceful community , this property promises tranquil living while being conveniently located.
